---
title: Trader Joe's Meatballs
source: https://www.traderjoes.com/home/products/pdp/italian-style-meatballs
tags: chicken, kid-friendly, quick and easy
servings: 4
cook time: 25 minutes
ai_image: true
date added: 2026-03-17
---

Preheat oven to 375°F. Spread @Trader Joe's Italian Style Meatballs{1%bag} in a single layer on a #rimmed baking sheet{}. Bake from frozen until heated through and browned, about ~{20%minutes}.

Meanwhile, warm @marinara sauce{1%jar} in a #saucepan{} over medium-low heat. Serve meatballs over @spaghetti{} or with crusty bread, topped with sauce and @Parmesan cheese{}.
